Description
In a distant, but not so unrealistic, future where mankind has abandoned earth because it has become covered with garbage, WALL-E, a garbage collecting robot has been left to clean up the mess. WALL-E is alone on Earth except for a sprightly pet cockroach. One day, EVE, a sleek (and dangerous) reconnaissance robot, is sent to Earth to find proof that life is once again sustainable. WALL-E falls in love with EVE. A so begins a amazing adventure of rescue, drama and romance.
